            "message": "<strong>Carousel Types:<\/strong><ul><li><strong>Standard:<\/strong> Traditional carousel with navigation arrows and dots. Shows 1-3 images at a time based on screen size.<\/li><li><strong>Continuous Scroll:<\/strong> Infinite horizontal scrolling animation. Perfect for logos or partner galleries.<\/li><\/ul><strong>Responsive Behavior (Standard):<\/strong><ul><li><strong>Desktop:<\/strong> 3 images visible<\/li><li><strong>Tablet:<\/strong> 2 images visible<\/li><li><strong>Mobile:<\/strong> 1 image visible<\/li><\/ul><strong>Features:<\/strong><ul><li>Optional image captions<\/li><li>Autoplay with hover pause<\/li><li>Customizable speed<\/li><li>Touch\/swipe support<\/li><li>Lazy loading ready<\/li><\/ul><strong>Best Practices:<\/strong><ul><li>Use consistent image dimensions<\/li><li>Optimize images for web (max 2MB)<\/li><li>Recommended: 1200x800px for standard carousel<\/li><li>Add alt text for accessibility<\/li><\/ul>",
